Masanin, Tiffany Ng daga Jami'ar Michigan, ya kuma bayyana cewa shi ne kararrawa ta farko a duniya da za a yi wa mawaƙin bakar fata, Dionisio A. Lind, wanda ya koma babban kararrawa a Cocin Riverside shekaru 18 da suka gabata.
Mista Merriweather ya ce St. Martin ba zai maye gurbinsa ba.
Abin da aka yi a St. Martin a cikin 'yan watannin nan ya zama abin ƙyama ga gine-ginen da masu aikin gine-gine, wasu shugabannin cocin ne suka kawo su, wasu kuma bishop na Episcopal.
Wuri na Vestry - hukumar gudanarwa ta ikilisiya, wacce ta kunshi shugabannin jama'a - ta rubuta wa bishop a watan Yuli da damuwa cewa bishop "zai yi kokarin amincewa da kudin" don dakin vestry, duk da cewa dakin vestry bai shiga cikin aikin gine-gine da masu kwangila da bishop ya kawo ba.
Wasu cikin ikilisiyar sun yi gunaguni game da rashin nuna gaskiya a cikin bishop's department.
