Sainsbury's na shirin shiga kasuwar kyakkyawa a Burtaniya
Sainsbury's ta ɗauki Boots, Superdrug da Debenhams daga ɗakin salon ado a cikin ɗakunan ajiya waɗanda ƙwararrun mataimakan ke sarrafawa.
A wani bangare na kokarin shiga kasuwar kyakkyawa ta fam biliyan 2.8 a Burtaniya, wacce ke ci gaba da bunkasa yayin da tallace-tallace na kayan kwalliya da kayan gida ke dawowa, za a gwada manyan wuraren kyawawan abubuwa a gidaje 11 a duk faɗin ƙasar kuma za a kai su zuwa ƙarin gidaje masu yawa a shekara mai zuwa idan ya yi nasara.
Sa hannun jari a cikin kayan ado ya bayyana yayin da manyan kasuwanni ke neman hanyoyin da za su yi amfani da ɗakunan da aka riga aka yi wa TV, microwave da kayan gida.
Sainsbury's ta ce za ta ninka adadin kayayyakin da take samarwa har zuwa 3,000, ciki har da kayayyaki kamar Revlon, Essie, Tweezerman da Dr. PawPaw a karon farko.
Abubuwan da ke akwai na L'Oreal, Maybelline da Burt's Bees za su sami ƙarin sarari tare da ɓangarorin iri ɗaya kamar waɗanda ake samu a shagunan kamar Boots.
Kasuwanci sun sake ƙaddamar da kayayyakin kwalliyar Boutique don yawancin samfuran su zama masu sada zumunta - wani abu da ke samun karuwar buƙata daga masu siye daga matasa.
Bugu da ƙari, dillalin turare mai suna Fragrance Shop zai gwada yarjejeniya a manyan kantuna biyu na Sainsbury's, wanda ya fara a Croydon, kudancin London, makon da ya gabata yayin da na biyu ya buɗe a Selly Oak, Birmingham, a ƙarshen wannan shekara.
Sayen kan layi da kuma sauya zuwa sayen abinci a gidajen abinci na gida na yau da kullum na nufin cewa manyan kasuwanni suna bukatar su yi aiki tuƙuru don shawo kan mutane su zo.
Mike Coupe, shugaban kamfanin Sainsbury's, ya ce, wannan shagon zai zama kamar babban gini, saboda manyan kantunan sayar da kayayyaki suna kokarin yin hamayya da manyan kamfanonin Aldi da Lidl, tare da samar da kayayyaki da ayyuka da yawa da ba na abinci ba.
Sainsbury's ya sanya reshen Argos a daruruwan shagunan kuma ya gabatar da wasu wurare tun lokacin da ya sayi duka sarkar biyu shekaru biyu da suka gabata, ana cewa ya inganta tallace-tallace na kantin sayar da kayayyaki kuma ya sa sayayya ta zama mai fa'ida.
Kasuwannin sun yi kokarin gyara bangarorin kayan kwalliya da na magani da suka kasa.
Sainsbury's ta gwada irin wannan aikin tare da Boot a farkon 2000, amma haɗin gwiwar ya ƙare bayan jayayya game da yadda za a raba kudaden shiga daga kantin sayar da magunguna a kasuwar ta.
Sabon dabarun ya bayyana ne bayan da Sainsbury ya sayar da kantin sayar da magunguna 281 ga Celesio, mai mallakar Lloyds Pharmacy, na fam miliyan 125 shekaru uku da suka gabata.
Ya ce Lloyds na da hannu a shirin, inda ya kara wasu manyan kayayyakin fata da suka hada da La Roche-Posay da Vichy a cikin gine-gine hudu.
Paul Mills-Hicks, darektan kasuwanci na Sainsbury's, ya ce: "Mun gyara kamannin da kuma yanayin da ke cikin dakinmu na ado don inganta yanayin da muke yi wa abokan cinikinmu.
Mun kuma zuba jari a cikin abokanmu da aka koyar musamman domin su ba da shawara.
An tsara kayayyakinmu da yawa don su dace da kowane irin bukata, kuma yanayinmu mai kyau da kuma wurin da muke da shi yana nufin cewa yanzu mun zama inda ake son yin ado da kyau da ke ƙalubalantar yadda ake cin kasuwa a dā".
Peter Jones ya yi 'yanci bayan Holly Willoughby ta janye £11m
Peter Jones, tauraron Dragon's Den, ya yi 'yanci bayan da mai gabatar da gidan talabijin Holly Willoughby ta janye yarjejeniyar fam miliyan 11 da ta yi da kamfanonin sayar da kayayyakin salon rayuwarta domin mayar da hankali kan sabon kwangilarta da Marks & Spencer da ITV
Willoughby ba shi da lokaci don kayan gida da kayan haɗi daga Truly Brand.
Gwyneth Paltrow ta kwatanta kasuwancin ma'auratan da alamar Goop.
Mai gabatar da shirin This Morning, mai shekara 37, ya yi amfani da Instagram don sanar da cewa zai daina.
Holly Willoughby ta bar tauraron Dragons Den, Peter Jones, cikin fushi ta janye daga kasuwancin kasuwancin salon salon salon rayuwa a lokacin ƙarshe - don mai da hankali kan sabon kwangilarta mai ban mamaki tare da Marks & Spencer da ITV.
Majiyoyi sun ce Jones ta yi "bacin rai" lokacin da jarumar ta bayyana a wani taro mai cike da tashin hankali a ranar Talata a hedkwatar masarautar kasuwancin ta a Marlow, Buckinghamshire, cewa sabon tayin da ta yi - wanda ya kai fam miliyan 1.5 - na nufin ba ta da lokacin da za ta sadaukar da kayayyakin gida da kayan haɗi daga Truly.
An yi la'akari da kasuwancin da Gwyneth Paltrow ta yi na Goop kuma ana sa ran zai ninka dukiyar Willoughby na £11m.
Lokacin da Willoughby, mai shekara 37, ya yi amfani da Instagram don sanar da cewa zai bar Truly, Jones ya tashi daga Birtaniya zuwa daya daga cikin wuraren hutu.
Majiya ta ce: "A duk tsawon lokacin, Truly ta kasance babban abin da ya fi muhimmanci a rayuwar Holly.
Zai kasance makomar ta na dogon lokaci wanda zai iya ganin ta cikin shekaru masu zuwa.
Shawarar janye duk wanda ya shiga cikin lamarin abin mamaki ne.
Ba wanda zai iya gaskata abin da ya faru a ranar Talata, yana kusa da kaddamarwa.
Akwai ɗaki cike da kayayyaki a hedkwatar Marlow da aka shirya don sayarwa".
Masana sun yi imanin cewa, ficewar mai gabatar da wannan jaridar, wanda ke cikin fitattun 'yan jarida a bankin Birtaniya, zai iya jawo asarar miliyoyin kamfanoni saboda zuba jari mai yawa a kayayyakin da suka hada da matashin kai da kyandir har zuwa tufafi da kayan gida, kuma yana iya jinkirta ƙaddamar da shi.
Kuma zai iya kawo ƙarshen wannan abokantaka.
Willoughby, mahaifiyar 'ya'ya uku kuma mijinta Dan Baldwin sun kasance abokai da Jones da matarsa Tara Capp na tsawon shekaru goma.
Willoughby ya kafa Truly tare da Capp a 2016 kuma Jones, 52, ya shiga shi a matsayin shugaban a watan Maris.
Ma'auratan suna hutu tare kuma Jones yana da kashi 40% na hannun jari a Baldwin, wani kamfanin samar da TV.
Willoughby zai zama jakadan alama ga M&S kuma zai maye gurbin Ant McPartlin a matsayin lauya na ITV a cikin shirin I'm A Celebrity.
Wani majiya da ke kusa da Jones ya ce a daren jiya "Ba za mu yi sharhi game da harkokin kasuwancinsa ba".
