Shugaban Mexico, AMLO ya yi alkawarin ba zai yi amfani da soji ba wajen kai hari kan fararen hula.
Shugaban kasar Mexico Andres Manuel Lopez Obrador ya yi alkawarin cewa ba zai yi amfani da soji ba a kan fararen hula yayin da kasar ke gabatowa da cika shekaru 50 da daukar fansa a kan mummunan bala'in da aka yi wa dalibai.
AMLO ta yi alkawari a Plaza Tlatelolco ranar Asabar cewa ba za ta taba amfani da sojoji ba don hana 'yan Mexico.
Sojoji sun harbi fararen hula da ke gudanar da zanga-zanga a kan wannan dandalin a ranar 2 ga watan Oktoba, 1968, wanda ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar fararen hula 300 yayin da ƙungiyoyin 'yan siyasa na hagu suka fara tasowa a ko'ina cikin Latin Amurka.
AMLO ta yi alkawarin tallafa wa matasa na Mexico ta hanyar ba da tallafin kowane wata ga waɗanda ke karatu da kuma buɗe ƙarin jami'o'in jama'a kyauta.
Ya ce rashin aikin yi da rashin samun ilimi ne ke janyo matasa su shiga cikin 'yan bindiga.
Ya kamata Amurka ta ninka kudaden da take bayarwa don yin amfani da hankali na wucin gadi.
"Dole ne Amurka ta ninka yawan kudade a fannin kere kere saboda kasar Sin na kara shiga cikin fannin", in ji Kai-Fu Lee, wani mai zuba jari da kuma mai amfani da kere kere da ya yi aiki a Google, Microsoft da Apple.
An bayyana ra'ayin ne bayan da gwamnatin Amurka ta yi sanarwa game da ilimin kere kere duk da cewa Amurka kanta gaba daya ba ta da wata dabara ta kere kere.
A halin yanzu, kasar Sin ta gabatar da shirin ta a bara inda ta yi niyyar zama kasa ta farko a fannin kirkirar kere kere ta hanyar fasaha nan da shekarar 2030.
"Abin da ya fi kyau shi ne a fara bincike a kan ilimin kere kere, domin sauran kasashen duniya sun yi kasa da Amurka, kuma muna son samun nasarar nan gaba a fannin ilimin kere kere", in ji Lee.
"Ta hanyar ninka kudaden da ake bayarwa zai iya kara samun damar samun babbar damar kera kere kere (AI) a Amurka", in ji Lee a wata hira da CNBC a wannan makon.
Littafin Lee mai suna AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and New World Order an buga shi a wannan watan ta Houghton Mifflin Harcout wanda shine Shugaba na Sinovation Ventures wanda ya saka hannun jari a daya daga cikin shahararrun kamfanonin kasar Sin, Face++.
A cikin shekarun 1980s, ya yi aiki a kan tsarin ilimin kere kere wanda ya doke dan wasan Othello na Amurka wanda ke kan gaba a lokacin da yake karatu a Jami'ar Carnegie Mellon. Daga baya, ya zama babban jami'i a Microsoft Research da kuma shugaban kamfanin Google na kasar Sin.
Lee ya amince da gasar fasahar gwamnatin Amurka da ta gabata kamar Robot Challenge daga Hukumar Cibiyar Binciken Ci Gaban Tsaro kuma yana son sanin lokacin da za a gudanar da gasar ta gaba don ya iya gano sabbin baiwa.
"Masu bincike a Amurka suna bukatar su yi aiki tukuru domin su samu tallafin gwamnati", in ji Lee.
"Ba kasar Sin ce ke daukar shugabannin ilimi ba, kamfanoni ne", in ji Lee.
Facebook, Google da sauran kamfanonin fasaha sun yi amfani da manyan baiwa daga jami'o'i don yin aiki a kan ilimin kere kere a 'yan shekarun nan.
Lee ya ce sauyin manufofin shige da fice na iya taimaka wa Amurka wajen tallafawa ayyukanta na leken asiri.
"Ina ganin ya kamata a ba da Green Card ta atomatik ga masu neman digirin digirgir a fannin ilimin kere kere", in ji shi.
Majalisar Jiha ta kasar Sin ta fitar da Shirin Ci gaban Artificial Intelligence na Zamani a watan Yulin 2017.
"Gidauniyar kimiyyar kasa ta kasar Sin tana ba da kudade ga masu ilimi, kamar yadda National Science Foundation da sauran hukumomin gwamnati ke ba da kudade ga masu bincike a Amurka, amma ingancin aikin kimiyya a kasar Sin ya fi na kasar Sin".
A farkon wannan shekarar, Ma'aikatar Tsaro ta Amurka ta kafa Cibiyar Hadin gwiwar Artificial Intelligence wanda ke da niyyar tattara abokan tarayya daga masana'antu da ilimi. Fadar White House ta sanar da jerin gwano na Kwamitin Zaɓaɓɓu don Artificial Intelligence.
A wannan watan, DARPA ta sanar da zuba jari na dala biliyan biyu a wani shiri da ake kira AI Next.
Kuma NSF tana zuba sama da dala miliyan 100 a shekara a binciken AI.
