Amma dai yawan masu jefa kuri'a ya kai kashi 16 cikin dari a zaben 2016 na majalisar dokoki, bayan da kashi 66 cikin 100 na masu jefa kuri'a suka jefa kuri'a.
"Na zo ne domin 'ya'yana, domin inda muke a Turai", in ji Gjose Tanevski, mai shekara 62, mai kada kuri'a a babban birnin kasar Skopje.
Firayim Ministan Macedonia Zoran Zaev, matarsa da ɗansu Dushko sun jefa kuri'a a Macedonia don sauya sunan ƙasar da zai buɗe hanyar Macedonia don shiga NATO da EU a Strumica, Macedonia a ranar 30 ga Satumba, 2018.
