Kalanda: Wanda ya kirkiro na'urar lissafin Geiger
Kuma yanzu, shafi daga kalandarmu ta "Safiya ta Lahadi": 30 ga Satumba, 1882, shekaru 136 da suka wuce a yau, kuma KYAUTA... ranar da aka haifi masanin kimiyyar lissafi Johannes Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger a Jamus.
Geiger ya kirkiro wata hanya ta gano da kuma auna radiyo, wanda hakan ya kai ga na'urar da ake kira Geiger Calculator.
A matsayin tushen kimiyya tun daga lokacin, Geiger counter ya zama kashin bayan al'adun gargajiya, kamar a cikin fim din "Bells of Coronado" a 1950, wanda ya hada da masanan kimiyya Roy Rogers da Dale Evans:
Mutum: "Mene ne wannan?"
Rogers: "Wannan na'urar mai auna Geiger ce, ana amfani da ita wajen gano ma'adanai masu guba, kamar su uranium.
Idan ka saka wannan, za ka iya jin tasirin da rediyo ke yi a cikin ma'adinai".
Evans: Haka ne, yana da kyau yanzu!
"Hans" Geiger ya mutu a shekara ta 1945, 'yan kwanaki kafin ya cika shekara 63.
Amma abin da ya sa ya zama haka ya ci gaba da wanzuwa.
Sabon allurar rigakafin cutar kansa na iya koya wa tsarin garkuwar jiki ta "duba" ƙwayoyin cuta
Sabuwar allurar rigakafin cutar kansa za ta iya koya wa tsarin garkuwar jiki ta "duba" ƙwayoyin cuta kuma ta kashe su
Rigakafin yana koya wa jikin mutum ya gane kwayoyin cutar a matsayin wani ɓangare na magani
Hanyar da ake amfani da ita ita ce, cire ƙwayoyin cuta daga cikin marasa lafiya, canza su a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje.
Yana iya ganin sunadarai da suka saba da kwayoyin cutar kansa da yawa kuma ya sake saka su
Alluran rigakafin gwaji sun nuna sakamako mai ban sha'awa ga marasa lafiya da ke da nau'ikan ciwon daji.
Wata mata da aka yi mata allurar rigakafi, wadda take koyar da tsarin garkuwar jikinta ta gane kwayoyin cutar, ta warke daga cutar kansa ta mahaifa bayan fiye da watanni 18.
Wannan hanyar tana ɗaukan ƙwayoyin cuta daga marasa lafiya, tana canja su a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje don su iya "ganin" wani furotin da ke da alaƙa da yawancin nau'in ciwon daji da ake kira HER2, kuma daga baya a sake saka ƙwayoyin.
Farfesa Jay Berzofsky, na Cibiyar Kula da Ciwon Ciwon daji ta Amirka a Bethesda, Maryland, ya ce: "Sakamakon gwajinmu ya nuna cewa muna da rigakafi mai kyau".
"HER2 tana haifar da ciwon daji da dama", har da na nono, na mahaifa, na huhu da kuma na hanji", in ji Farfesa Berzofsky.
Irin wannan tsarin da ake amfani da shi wajen kwayar jikin mutum da kuma koyar da su yadda za su kai wa kwayoyin cutar kansa hari ya yi nasara wajen magance cutar sankarar bargo.
Kanye West ya shiga cikin wani taron nuna goyon bayan Trump, yana saka hat na MAGA, bayan fitowar sa a SNL.
Ba a Amince da Su Ba
Kanye West ya yi ba'a a cikin studio a lokacin Saturday Night Live bayan wani babban wasan kwaikwayon inda ya yaba wa shugaban Amurka Donald Trump kuma ya ce zai yi takara a 2020.
Bayan da ta yi waka ta uku a daren mai taken "Ghost Town" inda ta saka hat ɗin "Make America Great", ta ci gaba da adawa da 'yan Democrat kuma ta sake jaddada goyon bayanta ga Trump.
"Na tambayi fararen fata sau da yawa kuma sun ce, 'Ta yaya za ku goyi bayan Trump, shi dan wariyar launin fata ne?'
"Ku sani, idan na damu game da wariyar launin fata, na riga na bar Amurka tun da daɗewa", in ji ta.
SNL ta fara wasan kwaikwayon ne da wani fim mai suna Matt Damon inda tauraron Hollywood din ya yi ta kokawa da Brett Kavanaugh a gaban kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa game da zargin cin zarafin da Christine Blasey Ford ta yi.
Ko da yake ba a watsa shi ba, an wallafa wani bidiyo na Kanye West a shafukan sada zumunta ta hanyar Chris Rock.
Ba mu san ko Rock yana son ya yi wa West ba'a da wannan aika-aikar ba.
Har ila yau, West ya yi korafi ga masu sauraro cewa ya sami matsala a bayan fage game da hat.
"Suna yi mini ba'a a bayan fage.
Suka ce, 'Kada ka fita can da wannan hat.'
Sun yi mini fyade!
Sai suka ce, "Ina cikin wani wuri da ba shi da muhimmanci", in ji shi, a cewar Washington Examiner.
West ya kara da cewa, "Kuna son ganin wannan matsayi na rashin muhimmanci?" yana cewa zai sa rigar Superman, domin hakan na nufin ba za ku iya jagorantar ni ba.
Ka yi kokarin kauna"
Maganganunsa sun jawo ba'a a kalla sau biyu daga masu sauraro kuma 'yan wasan SNL sun kasance masu kunya, in ji Variety, tare da wani a wurin ya gaya wa mai wallafa: "Dukkanin studio sun yi shiru".
An shigar da West a matsayin mai maye gurbin Ariana Grande, inda tsohon saurayinta, mawaki Mac Miller ya mutu kwanakin baya.
West ya ba da mamaki ga mutane da yawa tare da yin wasa da "I Love it", wanda ya yi ado a matsayin Perrier Bottle.
West ta samu goyon baya daga shugaban kungiyar TPUSA mai ra'ayin mazan jiya, Candace Turner, wanda ya aika da wasikar: "Ga daya daga cikin mutane masu karfin zuciya: Godiya ga ku don tsayawa kan masu sukar".
Amma a cikin wata sanarwa daga mai gabatar da shirin, Karen Hunter ta ce West "yana zama kansa ne kawai kuma abin farin ciki ne".
"Amma na zabi BA zan saka wa wani (ta hanyar sayen kiɗa ko tufafi ko tallafawa "fasaha") wanda na yi imanin yana karɓar kuma yana raba akidar da ke cutar da al'ummarmu.
Ya riga ya fita.
Mu ma haka", in ji shi.
Kafin wasan kwaikwayon, mawaƙin ya sanar a shafin Twitter cewa ya canza sunansa, yana mai cewa yanzu ana kiransa "wanda aka sani da Kanye West".
Ba shi ne dan wasan farko da ya canza sunansa ba kuma ya bi diddy, wanda aka fi sani da Puff Daddy, Puffy da P Diddy.
Abokinsa, wani mawaki mai suna Snoop Dogg ya sauya sunansa zuwa Snoop Lion kuma tabbas waƙar tana nufin ɗan waƙar, Prince, wanda ya canza sunansa zuwa alama kuma daga baya kuma a matsayin mai zane wanda aka fi sani da Prince.
An tuhume shi da yunkurin kashe mutum a wani cin abinci da aka yi a Belfast.
An gurfanar da wani mutum mai shekara 45 da kisan kai bayan an yi wa wani mutum wuka a wani gidan cin abinci a gabashin Belfast ranar Juma'a.
Wannan lamari ya faru ne a garin Ballyhackamore, in ji 'yan sanda.
Ana sa ran mai kare ya bayyana a kotun majalisa ta Belfast a ranar Litinin.
Za a sake nazarin tuhumar da ake yi wa masu gabatar da kara.
Tauraruwar Game of Thrones, Kit Harington ta yi amfani da maganin cutar
Kit Harington ya shahara sosai game da rawar da ya taka a matsayin Jon Snow a cikin HBO's Game of Thrones.
Amma 'yar fim, mai shekara 31, ta yi watsi da ra'ayin da ake yi na jaruman maco, inda ta ce yadda ake nuna su a talabijin na nufin matasa sukan ji kamar suna bukatar su kasance masu karfi domin a girmama su.
Da yake magana da The Sunday Times Culture, Kit ta ce ta yi imanin 'wani abu ba daidai ba ne' kuma ta yi tambaya game da yadda za a magance matsalar cutarwa ta maza a zamanin #MeToo.
Kit, wanda kwanan nan ya auri jarumar wasan kwaikwayon na Game of Thrones, Rose Leslie, ma mai shekaru 31, ya yarda cewa yana jin 'mai karfi' game da magance matsalar.
'Ina jin na yi karfi a halin yanzu, ina ganin ina da laifi a cikinmu game da namiji,' in ji shi.
'Me muka koya wa maza yayin da suka girma, a cikin matsalolin da muke fuskanta a yanzu?'
Kit ya yi imanin cewa talabijin na iya zama sanadin ƙaruwar ƙwayoyin cuta masu guba saboda halayen da ke da ƙwari.
Ya daɗa: 'Menene na halitta kuma menene aka koyar?
Me ake koyarwa a talabijin, da kuma a kan titi, da ke sa yara maza su ji cewa dole ne su zama irin waɗannan mutane?
Ina tsammanin wannan ita ce babbar tambaya a yanzu - ta yaya za mu canza shi?
Domin akwai wani abu da ke damun matasa a yau.'
A cikin hirar, ya kuma yarda cewa ba zai yi wani wasan kwaikwayo na farko ko na gaba ba Game of Thrones lokacin da jerin ya ƙare a lokacin bazara, yana cewa ya 'ƙare daga filin yaƙi da dawakai'.
A watan Nuwamba, Kit za ta yi fim din sake fasalin fim din True West na Sam Shepard wanda ke ba da labarin wani mai shirya fim da dan uwansa, dan fashi.
A kwanan nan, jarumin ya bayyana cewa ya yi tunanin saduwa da matarsa, Rose, shine mafi kyawun abin da ya faru a Game of Thrones.
'Na sadu da matata a kan wannan shirin, don haka ta ba ni iyali na gaba kuma rayuwata ta fara daga nan,' in ji shi.
Rose ta yi fim din Ygritte, wanda Kit ya buga a matsayin Jon Snow, a cikin kyautar Emmy ta kyautar fim.
Ma'auratan sun yi aure a watan Yunin 2018 a gidan Leslie a Scotland.
HIV/AIDS: China ta bayar da rahoton karuwar kashi 14 cikin 100 na sababbin masu kamuwa da cutar
Kasar Sin ta sanar da karuwar kashi 14 cikin 100 na yawan mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da kuma cutar AIDS.
Fiye da mutane 820,000 ne suka kamu da cutar a kasar, in ji jami'an kiwon lafiya.
An samu sabbin mutane kusan 40,000 a cikin kwata na biyu na 2018 kadai.
Yawancin sababbin cututtuka suna faruwa ne ta hanyar jima'i, wanda ke nuna canji daga abin da ya faru a baya.
A al'ada, cutar HIV tana yaduwa cikin sauri a sassan kasar Sin ta hanyar kamuwa da cutar ta jini.
Amma adadin wadanda ke dauke da kwayar cutar HIV ta wannan hanyar ya ragu zuwa kusan babu, in ji jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin a wani taron da aka gudanar a lardin Yunnan.
Duk da haka, kowace shekara, adadin mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da AIDS a China ya ƙaru zuwa mutane 100,000.
Yaduwar cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce a cikin al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
Ba a ƙara sanya luwadi a matsayin laifi a ƙasar Sin a shekara ta 1997, amma ana ganin nuna bambanci ga mutanen da suke da jinsi ɗaya yana ƙaruwa.
Saboda tsattsauran ra'ayin da ake da shi a ƙasar, bincike ya nuna cewa kashi 70-90 na mazajen da suke yin jima'i da maza za su yi aure da mata.
Yawancin cututtuka suna faruwa ne saboda rashin kāriya ta jima'i a cikin dangantaka.
Tun 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samar da maganin cutar HIV ga kowa a duniya a matsayin wani bangare na kokarin magance matsalar.
Maxine Waters ta musanta cewa ma'aikatanta sun fitar da bayanan sanata GOP, tana mai cewa "karya ce mai hadari" da kuma "ka'idar makirci"
A ranar Asabar ne, 'yar majalisar wakilai ta Amurka Maxine Waters ta yi tir da zargin da ma'aikatanta suka yi na cewa sun wallafa bayanan sirri na wasu 'yan majalisar wakilai uku a shafin Wikipedia na 'yan majalisa.
Dan jam'iyyar Democrat na Los Angeles ya tabbatar da cewa an yada wannan karar ne ta hanyar 'yan kungiyar " ultra-right " da kuma shafin yanar gizo.
"Yaudara, yaudara da kuma wasu munanan yaudara", in ji Waters a cikin wata sanarwa a shafin Twitter.
An ba da rahoton cewa bayanin da aka watsa ya haɗa da adireshin gida da kuma lambar waya na Sanata Lindsey Graham na South Carolina, da Mike Lee da Orrin Hatch, duka biyu daga Utah.
Bayanan sun bayyana a yanar gizo a ranar Alhamis, wanda wani ba a san shi ba ya watsa a kan Capitol Hill yayin sauraron taron majalisar dattawa game da zargin cin zarafin jima'i da ake yi wa dan takarar babban alkalin kotun Brett Kavanaugh.
Wannan fitowar ta faru ne bayan wasu 'yan majalisar dattawa uku sun yi wa Kavanaugh tambayoyi.
Shafukan yanar gizo masu ra'ayin mazan jiya kamar su Gateway Pundit da RedState sun ba da rahoton adiresoshin IP da ke gano tushen aikawa da ke da alaƙa da ofishin Waters da kuma yada bayanan ma'aikatan Waters, in ji Hill.
"Wannan zargi ba shi da tushe kuma karya ne", in ji Waters.
"Ma'aikatana - waɗanda aka yi wa lalatattun zarge-zarge da suka shafi mutuntaka, sirri, da kuma tsaro - ba su da wata alaƙa da wannan ɓarnatar da bayanai.
Wannan zargi da ba shi da tushe ba ƙarya ne kuma yaudara ce".
Maganar Waters ta jawo suka kan layi, ciki har da tsohon sakataren gidan jaridar fadar White House Ari Fleischer.
"Wannan ƙin yarda yana da fushi", in ji Fleischer.
"Wannan ya nuna cewa ba shi da halayen da ya dace da 'yan majalisa.
Idan aka zargi wani da aikata wani abu da bai yi ba, ba za su iya yin fushi ba.
Ba za su iya yin tsayayya ba.
Ba za su iya tambayar dalilin da ya sa ake tuhumarsu ba.
Dole ne su kasance masu kwanciyar hankali".
Fleischer ya yi wannan magana ne yayin da yake kwatanta yadda Waters ya yi da kuma sukar da 'yan Democrat suka yi wa Mai Shari'a Kavanaugh, wanda masu sukar suka zargi da nuna rashin jin daɗi a lokacin sauraron shari'ar ranar Alhamis.
Omar Navarro, dan takarar Republican da ke neman kayar da Waters a zaben tsakiyar shekara, shi ma ya bayyana ra'ayinsa a shafin Twitter.
"Babban labari ne idan gaskiya ne", ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter.
A gaskiya, Waters ya ce ofishinsa ya sanar da "masu iko da hukumomin da ke da alhakin shari'a game da wannan zargin na karya.
"Za mu tabbatar da cewa masu laifin za su bayyana", in ji shi, "kuma za su ɗauki alhakin dukan ayyukan da za su iya zama masu ɓarna da haɗari ga kowa da kuma dukan ma'aikatanmu".
