Duk da haka, Johnny English mai ban sha'awa da kuma mai ban sha'awa yana da damar da zai iya lalata abubuwa a karo na biyu - sunan da ya nuna cewa ya kasance mai ban sha'awa mai ban sha'awa wanda aka tsara don masu sauraron fina-finai ba masu magana da harshen Turanci ba.
Shi ne, ba shakka, ɗan ɓoye ɗan leƙen asiri wanda ya yi wani abu mai ban mamaki don rage ƙarancin glamor na Clouseau, ɗan ɗan Mr. Bean kuma ɗan mawaƙa wanda ya ba da rubutu ga waƙar jigon Chariots of Fire a bikin buɗe wasannin Olympics na London na 2012.
Ya kuma sami wahayi daga wani ɗan yawon buɗe ido kuma ɗan leƙen asiri na duniya, Rowan Atkinson wanda ya taɓa bayyana a cikin tallan talabijin na Barclaycard da aka manta yanzu, ya bar rikici bayan haka.
