Ina son Johnny English yana zuwa wurin jirgin sama a cikin rigar yaƙi na zamanin da kuma fan fan a kan kwalkwali.
Atkinson yana da baiwa na wasan kwaikwayo na jiki, amma wasan kwaikwayon yana da matukar damuwa da ban mamaki, musamman ma fina-finai masu "mai tsanani" kamar 007 da Mission Impossible yanzu suna ba da labari a matsayin kayan su.
Abin dariya ya ji kamar an fi mayar da hankali ga yara fiye da manya, kuma a wurina kuskuren Johnny English ba shi da kyau kuma yana mai da hankali kan fina-finai na Atkinson a cikin mutum na Bean.
