Kuma wannan yana nufin Johnny English da kansa, wanda ya yi gurguzu kuma yanzu yana aiki a matsayin malamin makaranta a wasu wurare masu kyau, amma ya ba da darasi wanda bai dace da zama ɗan leƙen asiri ba: wasu kyawawan darussa a nan, saboda Turanci yana ba da ilimin leƙen asiri a makarantar kimiyya kamar School of Rock.
