Shin bikin na duniya ne kuma ya yi wani abu don rage talauci?
A ranar Asabar, birnin New York zai karbi bakuncin bikin bikin duniya na mutane, wani biki na shekara-shekara na kiɗa wanda ke da manyan taurari masu ban mamaki da kuma manufa mai girma kamar ta; kawo ƙarshen talauci a duniya.
Yanzu a shekara ta bakwai, bikin na Duniya zai ga dubun dubatan mutane sun taru a babban filin shakatawa na Central Park ba wai kawai don kallon masu wasan kwaikwayo kamar Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, amma don kara wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin burin taron na kawo karshen matsanancin talauci nan da shekarar 2030.
Bikin Duniya, wanda aka fara a shekarar 2012, ci gaba ne na The World Poverty Project, wata kungiya ta tallafi ta kasa da kasa da ke da nufin kawar da talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke adawa da talauci.
