Amurka za ta iya amfani da rundunar sojin ruwa a matsayin takunkumi don hana Rasha fitar da man fetur
Washington na iya "idan ya zama dole" ta yi amfani da rundunar sojin ruwa ta hana Rasha sayar da man fetur a kasuwannin da suka hada da yankin Gabas ta Tsakiya, in ji Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amurka Ryan Zinke a cewar wani rahoto da Washington Examiner ta fitar.
Zinke ya yi ikirarin cewa Rasha na shiga cikin Syria - kamar yadda aka sani, ta shiga cikin gayyatar gwamnatin Syria - don neman sabbin kasuwannin mai.
"Ina ganin cewa suna nan a yankin na Tsakiya ne domin su mallaki man fetur kamar yadda suka yi a gabashin Turai da kuma kudancin Turai", in ji shi.
Kuma a cewar jami'an, akwai hanyar da za a bi wajen magance wannan matsalar.
"Amurka tana da ikon, tare da rundunar sojin ruwanmu, ta tabbatar da cewa hanyoyin teku suna bude, kuma idan ya zama dole, ta hana su don tabbatar da cewa man su ba zai iya zuwa kasuwa ba", in ji shi.
Zinke ya yi wannan jawabi ne a wani taron da kungiyar masu amfani da makamashin mai ta shirya, kungiyar da ba ta cin riba ba ce, wadda ke bayyana kanta a matsayin "muryar masu amfani da man fetur" a Amurka.
Ya kuma kwatanta ayyukan Washington akan Rasha da Iran, yana mai jaddada cewa su ma daidai ne.
"Zaɓin tattalin arziki a kan Iran da Rasha ya fi ko ƙasa da ɗaya, yana shafar da maye gurbin mai", in ji shi, yayin da yake nufin Rasha ba ta da wani zaɓi kuma tare da tattalin arzikinta da ke dogaro da mai.
Wannan sanarwa ta fito ne a yayin da gwamnatin Trump ke kan aikin kara fitar da iskar gas mai narkewa zuwa Turai wanda ya fi arha ga masu amfani da shi a Turai, a maimakon Rasha.
A sakamakon haka, jami'an Trump, ciki har da shugaban Amurka, Donald Trump da kansa, sun yi kokarin shawo kan Jamus ta janye daga aikin Nord Stream 2 mai nauyi, wanda Trump ya ce zai sa Berlin ta zama makami ga Moscow.
Moscow ta sha cewa, aikin da ake kira da Nord Stream 2 mai darajar dala biliyan 11 zai kara karfin da ake da shi na bututun mai zuwa miliyan biliyan 110 kuma aikin tattalin arziki ne kawai.
Kremlin ya ce Washington tana da karfi sosai, kuma tana hana wannan aikin ne saboda dalilai na tattalin arziki, kuma misali ne na rashin adalci.
"Na tabbata mun yarda cewa ba za a iya amfani da samar da makamashi a matsayin makami na zalunci ba kuma masu amfani da shi ya kamata su sami 'yancin zabarsu", in ji Ministan makamashin Rasha Aleksandr Novak bayan ganawa da Sakataren makamashin Amurka Rick Perry a Moscow a watan Satumba.
Wannan matakin na Amurka ya jawo rashin jin daɗin Jamus, wacce ta sake tabbatar da jajircewarta ga wannan aikin.
Babban kungiyar masana'antu a Jamus, BDI, ta bukaci Amurka da kada ta shiga cikin manufofin makamashi na EU da kuma yarjejeniyar tsakanin Berlin da Moscow.
"Ina da matsala matuka idan wata kasa ta uku ta shiga cikin samar da makamashi a kasarmu", in ji Dieter Kempf shugaban kungiyar masana'antu ta Jamus (BDI) kwanan nan bayan ganawar da Angela Merkel ta yi da shugaban Rasha, Vladimir Putin.
Elizabeth Warren Za Ta Yi Tunanin Gasar Shugaban Kasa A 2020, Inji Sanatan Massachusetts.
Sanata Elizabeth Warren ta Massachusetts ta ce a ranar Asabar za ta yi tunani sosai kafin ta tsaya takarar shugaban kasa bayan zaben da za a yi a tsakiyar shekara mai zuwa.
A lokacin da aka yi wa mazauna Holyoke, Massachusetts tambayoyi, Warren ya ce zai yi la'akari da yin takara.
"Lokaci ya yi da mace za ta je Washington ta gyara gwamnatinmu da ta rabu kuma hakan ya hada da sanya mace a kan kujerar", in ji ta a cewar The Hill.
Bayan 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zan yi tunani sosai game da neman shugabancin kasar.
Warren ya bayyana damuwarsa game da shugaba Donald Trump a lokacin da aka yi masa tambayoyi, inda ya ce Trump yana kai kasarmu ga hanyar da ba ta dace ba.
"Ina damuwa da abin da Donald Trump ke yi wa dimokiradiyarmu", in ji shi.
Warren ya yi tir da Trump saboda ya zabi Brett Kavanaugh a matsayin dan takarar kotu.
A wata sanarwa da Warren ya fitar a ranar Juma'a, ya ce "da gaske ne muna bukatar binciken FBI kafin a yi zabe".
