Wanda ya kirkiro Yanar gizo Tim Berners-Lee ya kaddamar da kamfani na farko domin ya yi gogayya da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Sabon aikin wannan almara na fasaha, Inrupt, kamfani ne mai amfani da tushen tushen tushen tushen software na Solid wanda Berners-Lee ya kirkira.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda za a adana bayanan su da kuma wanda zai sami damar shiga bayanin.
A wata hira ta musamman da aka yi da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi wa dariya cewa ainihin manufar Inrupt ita ce "sarrafa duniya".
