A cewar jaridar London Gazette, a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, Laftanar Kanar Vann ta jagoranci rundunarsa ta tsallaka Canal de Saint-Quentin - wanda ke cike da hazo mai yawa kuma ya shawo kan harin injina.
Sai ya yi ta faman zuwa kan iyakar kasar da karfin hali ya yi ta kai hari kafin ya yi ta harbi da bindiga daya da kansa ya harbe mutane uku.
An kashe Lieutenant Colonel a hannun wani dan Jamus mai harbi a ranar 4 ga Oktoba, 1918 - wata daya kafin yakin ya ƙare.
Michael Vann, mai shekara 72, ya ce abin da ya yi ya sa ni farin ciki sosai.
Shi da dan uwansa Dr James Vann sun kuma sanya furanni bayan bikin wanda aka gudanar da gasar matasa ta Brentwood Imperial.
Micheal Vann ya ce "na ji daukaka sosai na shiga cikin wannan motsi" kuma ya kara da cewa "gaskiya ne ƙarfin hali tare da goyon bayan da mutane da yawa suka bayar".
MMA masu goyon baya sun zauna duk dare suna kallon Bellator 206, a maimakon haka an ba su Peppa Pig
Ka yi tunanin kana zaune a kan gado duk dare don ka kalli Bellator 206 amma ka yi sanyin gwiwa domin ka kalli ainihin wasan kwaikwayon.
Jerin wasannin 13 da aka yi a San Jose, ciki har da wasannin farko guda shida da za a watsa a duk daren a Burtaniya a tashar Channel 5.
Da karfe shida na safe, lokacin da Gegard Mousasi da Rory MacDonald ke shirin yin kara, masu sauraro a Burtaniya sun yi mamakin lokacin da aka sauya watsa shirye-shiryen zuwa Peppa Pig.
Wasu daga cikinsu sun yi fushi da cewa sun zauna a kan gado duk dare don kallon wannan wasan.
Wani mai sha'awar fim ya ce sauya tashar wasan yara "wani abin dariya ne da bai dace ba" a cikin bidiyonsa.
"Dokar gwamnati ta nuna cewa watsa shirye-shiryen karfe shida na safe ba su dace da wasanni ba don haka sai suka tilasta su watsa shirye-shiryen yara", in ji Dave Schwartz, babban mataimakin shugaban kasuwanci da sadarwa na Bellator lokacin da aka tambaye shi game da watsa shirye-shiryen.
"Khinzir ne mahaifinmu, haka ne".
Shugaban Bellator Scott Coker ya ce suna kokarin sake tsara shirin domin masu kallo a Burtaniya su iya kallon shi.
"Ina tsammanin, lokacin da na yi magana game da sake watsa shirye-shirye, ina tsammanin za mu iya yin wani abu", in ji Coker.
