An sake jinkirta sabon jirgin ruwan Jamus
Rundunar sojin ruwan Jamus ta kamata ta karbi sabon jirgin ruwan a shekarar 2014 domin maye gurbin jiragen yaki na zamanin Cold War, amma jirgin ba zai kammala ba har sai shekara mai zuwa saboda lalacewar tsarin da kuma hauhawar farashin, a cewar rahoton kafofin watsa labarai na kasar.
Aikin jirgin ruwan yaki Rhineland-Pfalz, jirgin farko a karkashin Baden-Wuerttemberg-class frigate yanzu an dage shi zuwa rabin shekarar 2019, a cewar jaridar Die Zeit da ke ambaton mai magana da yawun sojin.
Ya kamata jirgin ya shiga rundunar sojin ruwa a shekarar 2014, amma rashin alheri matsalar bayan mika shi ya shafi wannan babban aikin.
Dakarun sojan ruwa hudu na Baden-Wuerttemberg-class da Navy ta yi odar su a 2007 za su maye gurbin na Bremen-class.
An fahimci cewa, zai ƙunshi fasali kamar su manyan bindigogi, kayan aikin anti-jirgin sama da anti-jirgin ruwa da kuma wasu fasalolin ɓoye kamar rage radar, hasken wuta da kuma iyawar sauti.
Sauran mahimman abubuwan da suka dace sune tsawon lokacin kulawa - sabon frigate dole ne ya iya tafiya har zuwa shekaru biyu daga tushe.
Duk da haka, matsaloli da yawa sun nuna cewa wannan jirgin ruwan da ake ganin zai iya nuna ikon Jamus a ƙasashen waje zai zama tsohon yayi kafin ya shiga aikin Sojan Ruwa, in ji Die Zeit
Wannan mummunan jirgin ruwan F125 ya zama sanannen labarai a shekarar da ta gabata, lokacin da jami'an sojin ruwan Jamus suka ki amincewa da karbar jirgin yaƙi da kuma mayar da shi ga kamfanin ginin jiragen ruwa na Blohm & Voss a Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko da Sojojin Ruwa suka mayar da jirgin bayan sun kai shi.
Ba a san dalilin da ya sa aka mayar da jirgin ba, amma jaridar Jamus ta ce wasu matsaloli na software da na'ura sun sa jirgin ya zama mara amfani idan aka tura shi aikin yaƙi.
Rushewar software dole ne a ɗauka da nauyi saboda jirgin Baden-Wuerttemberg-class zai yi aiki da kawai 120 na'urori - rabin abin da ake bukata don sarrafa tsoffin jirgin ruwan Bremen.
Akwai kuma batun cewa jirgin ruwan yana da nauyi sosai kuma wannan zai rage aikin kuma ya iyakance ikon da Sojojin Ruwa ke da shi na yin kowane irin cigaba a nan gaba.
Jirgin ruwan Rhineland-Pfalz mai nauyin tan 7,000 ya yi kusan ninki biyu na jirgin ruwan da sojojin Jamus suka yi amfani da shi a lokacin yakin duniya na biyu.
Baya ga lalacewar na'urar, farashin aikin gaba ɗaya - gami da horo don ƙwallon ƙafa - ma batun ne.
An ce an kashe Euro biliyan 3.1 ($3.6bn) a kan wannan aikin - wanda ya karu daga farashin farko na Euro biliyan 2.2.
Matsalar da ta shafi wannan sabon jirgin ruwan ya nuna yadda sojojin Jamus suka yi kasa.
A farkon wannan shekarar, Hans-Peter Bartels, shugaban kwamitin tsaro na majalisar dattawa ya yarda cewa sojojin ruwa na fuskantar matsalar rashin jiragen ruwa masu karfin gaske.
