Hukuncin da aka gabatar, gami da rage tallafin kudi da kuma takunkumin biza da aka tsara, zai yi mummunar tasiri ga kasar ta Amurka ta tsakiya tare da yawan cin zarafi da kisan kai.
Bayan an gudanar da taron cikin gida, jami'an Arewacin Amurka da na Amurka ta Tsakiya sun dage wani babban taron da ya mayar da hankali kan tsaro da wadata ta tattalin arziki, don bin diddigin irin wannan taron na bara wanda ya zama kamar wani mataki ne mai kyau na hana bakin haure zuwa Amurka.
Amma a tsakiyar watan Satumba, manyan jami'an gwamnati sun yanke shawarar cewa suna son a ci gaba da taron, a zahiri sun dakatar da duk wani tunani na ci gaba da tara El Salvador.
Mataimakin shugaban kasa Mike Pence zai gabatar da jawabin a taron, wanda aka tsara a tsakiyar watan Oktoba, a matsayin alamar shigo da mukamin gwamnati a cikin taron, a cewar jami'an.
Kuma wakilai uku na Amurka sun koma El Salvador, Panama da Jamhuriyar Dominica ba tare da wata sanarwa ko wata hukunci daga Washington ba.
Mai magana da yawun fadar White House na Bolton ya ki yin tsokaci kan cikakkun bayanai na muhawara da jami'an Amurka uku suka bayyana, ciki har da wasu jami'an diflomasiyya biyu da suka amince su tattauna batun na cikin gida ba tare da an bayyana sunansu ba.
An tabbatar da bayanin da wasu manazarta na waje da ke da kusanci da gwamnatin suka yi, kuma sun yi magana ne bisa ga sunayensu.
