Girgizar kasa da tsunami a Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka rasa rayukansu sakamakon girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta afkawa birnin Palu na kasar Indonesia ranar Juma'a, kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu, a cewar hukumomi.
Ba tare da samun hanyar sadarwa ba, hukumomi ba su iya samun bayanai daga gwamnatin Donggala, yankin arewacin Palu da ke kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasar mai karfin awo 7.5.
A Palu, mutane sama da 16,000 ne aka kwashe bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala, a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu shine babban birnin lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya, wanda ke a ƙarshen bakin tekun a gabar yamma ta tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da mazaunan 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
An yi bikin cika shekaru 40 da haihuwar wannan birni a lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka afkawa birnin.
Donggala yanki ne mai mulki mai nisan kilomita 300 (180 mi) a gabar tekun arewa maso yammacin Sulawesi.
Yankin da ke karkashin wannan yanki, wanda ke karkashin yankin, yana da yawan mutane 299,200 a shekarar 2017.
Kamun kifi da kiwo sune kashin bayan tattalin arzikin yankin na Central Sulawesi, musamman a yankin ruwan Donggala.
Ma'adinan nickel ma yana da mahimmanci a cikin yankin, amma kawai yana da hankali a Morowali, a bakin tekun da ke fuskantar Sulawesi.
Palu da Donggala sun sha fama da Tsunami sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100, a cewar Hukumar Rage Bala'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗarurruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Tsunami ya kuma afkawa yammacin Donggala a shekarar 1996, inda ya yi sanadiyyar mutuwar mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin Pacific Ring of Fire kuma tana fama da girgizar kasa.
Ga wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka auku a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a yammacin yankin Acheh, Indonesia a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga Disamba ta haifar da tsunami da ya afkawa kasashe 14, ya kashe mutane 226,000 a duk fadin ruwan Tekun Indiya, rabin adadin a Aceh.
2005: Wani girgizar kasa mai girgiza ta afkawa gabar yammacin Sumatra a karshen watan Maris da farkon watan Afrilu.
An kashe daruruwan mutane a tsibirin Nias da ke gabar tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 6.8 ta afka kudu da Java, tsibirin da ya fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta haifar da tsunami da ya afkawa gabar tekun kudu, ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.6 ta afkawa kusa da garin Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma.
Fiye da mutane 1,100 suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.5 ta afkawa daya daga cikin tsibiran Mentawai, a Sumatra, ta haifar da tsunami mai tsawon mita 10 da ya lalata kauyuka da dama da kuma kashe mutane 300.
2016: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa yankin Pidie Jaya na Acheh, inda ta haifar da bala'i da fargaba, tunatar da mazauna yankin game da mummunan girgizar kasa da tsunami da aka yi a 2004.
Babu wata tsunami da aka yi a lokacin, amma sama da mutane 100 ne suka rasa rayukansu a sakamakon rushewar gine-ginen.
2018: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok na Indonesia, inda ta yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane sama da 500, musamman a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon bude ido a cikin wani yanayi na wucin gadi.
An tsare ɗan fari na Sarah Palin bisa zargin cin zarafin cikin gida
An kama Track Palin, ɗan fari na tsohon gwamnan Alaska, kuma mai neman shugabancin kasar Sarah Palin, bisa zargin kai hari.
An kama Palin, mai shekara 29, daga Wasilla, Alaska, bisa zargin aikata hare-hare na gida, hana rahoton laifukan ta'addanci na gida da kuma adawa da tsare, a cewar wani rahoto da Alaska State Troopers ta fitar a ranar Asabar.
A cewar rahoton 'yan sanda, lokacin da abokiyar matar ta yi kokarin yin kiran 'yan sanda don bayar da rahoton laifin, sai ya kwace wayar daga hannun matar.
An kama Palin a gidan kotun Mat-Su inda aka kama ta da wata takardar da ba a ba ta ba, wadda ta kai dala 500.
An gurfanar da shi a kotu a ranar Asabar, inda ya amsa cewa "ba shi da laifi" lokacin da aka tambaye shi game da ikirarinsa, in ji hanyar sadarwa.
Palin na fuskantar laifuffuka uku na aji A, wanda ke nufin za a iya daure shi har shekara guda a kurkuku kuma a ci masa tarar dala 250,000.
An kuma tuhume shi da laifin laifi mai daraja B, wanda za a iya yanke masa hukuncin kwana ɗaya a kurkuku da kuma tarar dala dubu biyu.
Wannan ba shi ne karo na farko da aka tuhumi Palin da aikata laifi ba.
A watan Disamba na 2017, an zargi matashin da kai hari ga mahaifinsa, Todd Palin.
Mahaifiyarta, Sarah Palin, ta kira 'yan sanda don su kai karar harin.
An kai wannan shari'ar a Kotun Sojojin Alaska.
A watan Janairun 2016, an tuhume shi da aikata hare-hare na cikin gida, tsangwama ga rahoton laifukan ta'addanci na cikin gida da kuma mallakar makamai a cikin maye dangane da lamarin.
Abokinta ta ce mutumin ya buge ta.
