Masu gabatar da kara na neman hukuncin kisa na musamman ga wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci na birnin New York.
Babban Lauyan New York na neman hukuncin kisa ga Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci na New York City wanda ya kashe mutane takwas-- hukuncin da ba a taba yankewa a jihar ba, wanda aka kira don aikata laifuka na tarayya tun 1953.
An zargi Saipov, mai shekara 30, da amfani da motar haya ta Home Depot don kai hari a kan hanyar keke a kan titin West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan, inda ya yi wa masu tafiya da ƙafa da masu hawan keke a kan hanyarsa a ranar Oct.
Don a tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara dole ne su tabbatar da cewa Saipov "ya yi niyyar" kashe wadanda aka kashe da kuma "yin niyyar" cutar da su, a cewar sanarwar da aka bayar da niyyar neman hukuncin kisa, da aka shigar a Kudancin District na New York.
An yanke hukuncin kisa a kan waɗannan laifuffuka biyu, bisa ga takardun kotu.
Makonni bayan harin, babban alkalin kotun tarayya ya tuhumi Saipov da laifuka 22 ciki har da laifukan kisa takwas da suka shafi ayyukan haram, wanda ake amfani da shi a lokuta da yawa a cikin shari'ar aikata laifuka, da kuma laifukan ta'addanci da lalata motoci.
Harin ya bukaci "shirye-shirye da kuma shiri mai kyau" wanda, a cewar mai gabatar da kara, ya nuna yadda Saipov ya aiwatar da ayyukansa a matsayin "mai zalunci, mai zalunci da kuma abin kunya".
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya yi sanadin rauni, azaba, da kuma rashi ga dangi da abokansa Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza, da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco", in ji sanarwar da aka yi niyya.
Biyar cikin waɗanda aka kashe baƙi ne daga ƙasar Argentina.
An yi kusan shekara biyu ana tuhumar mutane da hukuncin kisa a gundumar Kudancin New York.
An tuhumi wanda ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, da kisan wasu masu safarar miyagun kwayoyi guda biyu amma daga bisani aka yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai a watan Satumbar 2009.
Lokaci na ƙarshe da aka yanke hukuncin kisa a cikin shari'ar tarayya ta New York shine a 1953 ga Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka yanke musu hukuncin kisa bayan an yanke musu hukuncin yin leken asiri ga Soviet Union a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
An yanke wa Rosenberg hukuncin kisa ta hanyar amfani da wutar lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
