David Patton, daya daga cikin lauyoyin tsaro na tarayya da ke wakiltar Saipov, ya ce sun "yi matukar takaici" da hukuncin da mai gabatar da kara ya yanke.
"Mun ji cewa yanke shawarar neman hukuncin kisa maimakon karbar hukuncin daurin rai da rai ba tare da yiwuwar samun damar sakewa ba, kawai ya tsawaita raunin wannan lamarin ga duk wanda ya shiga ciki", a cewar Patton.
