Warren yana shirin yin nazari don ya yi takarar shugaban kasa
Sanata Elizabeth Warren ta ce za ta yi "binciken neman shugabanci" bayan zaben na watan Nuwamba.
Jaridar Boston Globe ta ruwaito cewa dan Democrat na Massachusetts ya gabatar da shirinsa na gaba yayin wani taron a garin West Massachusetts ranar Asabar.
Warren, mai sukar shugaban kasa Donald Trump, yana neman zaben sake zaben a watan Nuwamba tare da dan takarar GOP na jihar Geoff Diehl, wanda shi ne shugaban kungiyar Trump ta Massachusetts a shekarar 2016.
An yi hasashen cewa zai yi takarar Trump a 2020.
Taron da ya gudana a ranar Asabar a Holyoke shi ne karo na 36 da ya gana da masu sauraro a cikin salon taro na gari tun lokacin da Trump ya zama shugaban kasa.
Wani mai halarta ya tambaye shi ko yana son ya tsaya takarar shugaban kasa.
Warren ya ce, "Lokaci ya yi da mata za su je Washington don su gyara gwamnatin da ta lalace, kuma wannan ya haɗa da mace a kan mataki na farko".
An kama wani mutum a cikin harin da aka kashe Sims daga LSU
