Gasar Rasha: Lewis Hamilton ya kusa cin kofin duniya lokacin da tawagar ta umarce shi da ya lashe, ya doke Sebastian Vettel
A bayyane yake a lokacin, Valtteri Bottas ya yi nasara a gaban Lewis Hamilton a ranar Asabar, "martanin da Mercedes ta yi ya taka rawa sosai a wannan tseren.
Daga farkon farar hula, Bottas ya fara da kyau, ya kusan doke Hamilton yayin da yake kare matsayinsa a zagaye na farko da biyu kuma ya sa Vettel ya kai hari ga abokan aikinsa.
Vettel ya fara shiga cikin tukunyar kuma ya bar Hamilton a cikin zirga-zirga a ƙarshen rukuni, abin da ya kamata ya zama na ƙarshe.
Mercedes ta shiga cikin rami a zagaye na gaba kuma ta fita a bayan Vettel, amma Hamilton ya yi aiki a kan taya wanda ya bar Ferrari ya bar ciki ba tare da hadarin kare kansa ba bayan aikin karewa na uku.
Max Verstappen ya fara daga baya a kan grid kuma ya kasance a matsayi na bakwai bayan zagaye na farko a ranar haihuwarsa ta 21.
Daga nan sai ya jagoranci yawancin tseren kuma bai canza taya ba don yin saurin kawo karshen kuma ya tsallake Kimi Raikkonen don matsayi na huɗu.
Ya fara shiga cikin pit a zagaye na 44 amma bai iya haɓaka saurin ba don zagaye na gaba takwas lokacin da Raikkonen ya kasance a matsayi na huɗu.
Ranar wahala ce ga Valtteri wanda ya yi kyakkyawan tseren karshen mako kuma yana da halin kirki ya bar ni in yi tsalle.
"Kungiyoyin sun yi aiki mai kyau don lashe gasar farko da na biyu", in ji Hamilton.
Wannan shi ne harshen da ba shi da kyau.
Shugaba Donald Trump ya yi wa Sanata Dianne Feinstein ba'a a wani taro a ranar Asabar saboda wata mata da ta bukaci shi kada ya fitar da wata wasika daga Christine Blasey Ford da ta zargi dan takarar Majalisa Brett Kavanaugh da laifin cin zarafin mata.
Da yake jawabi a wani taro a West Virginia, shugaban bai ba da amsa kai tsaye ba game da shaidar da aka bayar a gaban kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa, maimakon haka ya yi sharhi cewa abin da ya faru a majalisar dattawa ya nuna mutane "masu zalunci da munana da kuma masu ƙarya".
"Abu daya da zai iya faruwa kuma abu mai kyau ya faru a kwanakin baya a majalisar dattijai, lokacin da ka ga fushi, lokacin da ka ga mutane masu fushi da mugunta da munana da kuma masu karya", in ji shi.
"Idan ka duba bayanan da suka zubo kuma suka ce "oh, ban yi ba.
Ban yi hakan ba".
Ka tuna da shi?
Dianne Feinstein, ka yi ɓoye?
Ka tuna amsar... shin ka fitar da takardun ne? "oh, oh, me?
Oh, ba haka ba.
Ban tona asirin ba".
To, jira na ɗan lokaci.
Shin mun leaked... A'a, ba mu leaked", ya kara da cewa, tare da yin da na sanata ta fuskar.
An aika wa Feinstein takardar da ke bayyana zargin da aka yi wa Kavanaugh Ford a watan Yuli, kuma an fitar da takardar a watan Satumba - amma Feinstein ya musanta cewa bayanan sun fito ne daga ofishinsa.
"Ban ɓoye zargin Dr. Ford ba, ban kuma ɓoye labarin ba", in ji Feinstein ga kwamitin, in ji The Hill.
"Ya ce in kiyaye shi a matsayin sirri kuma na kiyaye shi a matsayin sirri kamar yadda aka nema".
Amma shugaban bai ji daɗin wannan ƙin yarda da matar ba, wanda ya yi sharhi a taron ranar Asabar: "Ina gaya muku, wannan ba shi da kyau.
Wataƙila ba ya yin haka, amma wannan ita ce mafi munin yaren motsa jiki da na taɓa gani".
Da yake ci gaba da kare dan takarar na babban kotun, wanda aka zargi da laifin lalata da mata uku suka yi, shugaban ya ba da shawarar cewa 'yan Democrat za su yi amfani da zargin don cimma burinsu.
"Suna son su dawo da mulki ta kowace hanya.
Ka ga, zalunci, rashin mutunci, ba su damu da wanda suka ji rauni ba, wanda suka yi hadaya don samun iko da iko", in ji rahoton da Mediaite ya yi.
Ƙungiyar Elite: Dundee Stars 5-3 Belfast Giants
Patrick Dwyer ya ci kwallo a raga a Dundee
Tauraron Dundee ya rama rashin nasarar da ya yi a gasar Elite League a ranar Juma'a a kan Belfast Giants ta hanyar lashe wasan da suka yi a Dundee 5-3 a ranar Asabar.
Giants sun ci gaba da cin kwallaye biyu a raga ta hanyar bugun da Patrick Dwyer da Francis Beauvillier suka yi.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cownie sun daidaita matsayin masu masaukin baki kafin Dwyer ya dawo da Giants a kan nasara.
Francois Bouchard ya daidaita maki biyu ga Dundee kafin biyu daga Lukas Lundvald Nielsen ya tabbatar da nasara a gare su.
Wannan dai shi ne kashi na uku na gasar Elite League a kakar wasa ta bana ga tawagar Adam Keefe, wanda ya zo daga kasa don doke Dundee da ci 2-1 a Belfast ranar Juma'a da daddare.
Wannan shi ne karo na hudu da za a yi tsakanin bangarorin biyu a kakar wasa, inda Giants suka lashe wasanni uku da suka gabata.
Budewa ga Dwyer ya zo a minti na huɗu a 3:35 daga taimakon Kendall McFaull, tare da David Rutherford yana ba da taimako yayin da Beauvillier ya ninka gaba bayan minti huɗu.
Da abin da ya zama kamar lokacin buɗewa, Sullivan ya ɗaga maki a gida a 13:10 kafin Matt Marquardt ya zama mataimakin Cownie a daidai da 15:16.
Dwyer ya tabbatar da cewa Giants sun lashe wasan a lokacin hutu na farko lokacin da ya zira kwallaye biyu a daren a ƙarshen farkon.
Sai 'yan wasan suka sake haduwa, Bouchard ya sake daidaitawa da ci a 27:37.
Cownie da Charles Corcoran sun hada kai don taimakawa Nielsen ya ba Dundee nasara ta farko a wasan da ya yi a karo na biyu kuma ya tabbatar da nasarar tare da ƙungiyar ta biyar a tsakiyar lokaci.
Giants, wanda suka yi rashin nasara a wasanni hudu daga cikin biyar, suna gida, Milton Keynes domin karawa a ranar Juma'a.
Masu kula da zirga-zirgar jiragen sama sun rasa rayukansu domin tabbatar da cewa dubban mutane sun tsere daga jirgin.
Masu kula da zirga-zirgar jiragen sama a Indonesia sun yi farin ciki bayan da suka tabbatar da cewa jirgin da ke dauke da daruruwan fasinjoji ya tashi.
Fiye da mutane 800 ne suka rasa rayukansu kuma da dama sun bace bayan wata babbar girgizar kasa da ta afkawa tsibirin Sulawesi ranar Juma'a, ta haifar da tsunami.
Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta ci gaba da afkawa yankin kuma mutane da dama sun makale a cikin rugujewar da ta afkawa garin Palu.
Ko da yake abokin aikinsa ya tsere, mai shekaru 21 mai suna Anthonius Gunawan Agung, ya ki barin wurin kula da shi a hasumiyar kula da tashin hankali a Filin jirgin saman Pearl Sis Al Jufri, Palu.
Bai yi komai ba don tabbatar da cewa jirgin Batik Air 6321, wanda ke kan hanyarsa a lokacin, ya tashi lafiya.
Sai ya yi tsalle daga hasumiyar lokacin da ya ji cewa hasumiyar za ta rushe.
Ya mutu a asibiti.
Kakakin kamfanin jirgin sama na Indonesia, Yohannes Sirait, ya ce wannan matakin na iya ceton daruruwan rayuka, in ji ABC News Australia.
Mun shirya wani helikofta daga Balikpapan a Kalimantan don kai shi babban asibiti a wani birni.
Abin baƙin ciki, mun rasa shi a safiyar yau kafin jirgin sama ya isa Palu.
"Mun yi baƙin ciki da wannan labari", in ji shi.
A halin yanzu hukumomi na fargabar cewa adadin wadanda suka mutu zai iya kaiwa dubbai, yayin da hukumomin rage bala'in suka ce an takaita shiga garuruwan Donggala, Sigi da Boutong.
"Lambar mutuwar ta ci gaba da ƙaruwa saboda gawarwaki da dama da ke ƙarƙashin tarkace da kuma mutane da yawa da ba a iya tuntuɓarsu ba", in ji mai magana da yawun hukumar Sutopo Purwo Nugroho.
Ruwa mai tsawon mita 20 ya lalata Palu wanda zai yi jana'izar jama'a a ranar Lahadi.
Jiragen sama na soja da na kasuwanci za su kawo taimako da kayayyaki.
Risa Kusuma, wata mahaifiyar 'ya'ya 35, ta gaya wa Sky News cewa: "Kowane minti ana kawo gawa a asibiti.
Ruwa mai tsabta yana da wuya a samu.
An sake gina shaguna a ko'ina".
Jan Gelfand, shugaban kungiyar agaji ta kasa da kasa a Indonesia, ya shaida wa CNN cewa: "Kungiyar agaji ta kasa da kasa ta Indonesia ta gaggauta kai agaji ga wadanda suka tsira amma ba mu san abin da za mu samu a wurin ba.
Wannan bala'i ne, amma zai iya daɗa muni".
Shugaban Indonesia Joko Widodo, ya isa Palu a ranar Lahadi kuma ya gaya wa sojojin kasar: "Ina rokon ku da ku yi aiki dare da rana don kammala kowane aiki da ya shafi gudun hijira.
Kuna shirye?" In ji rahoton CNN.
An yi wa Indonesia wani girgizar kasa a farkon wannan shekara a Lombok inda ta kashe mutane sama da 550.
Hadarin jirgin saman Micronesia: Air Niugini ta ce yanzu haka fasinjan daya ya bace bayan jirgin ya fadi
Kamfanin jirgin da ke kula da jirgin da ya yi hatsari a tafkin Pacific a Micronesia ya ce yanzu haka ba a sami wani fasinja ba, bayan da ya ce an kwashe dukkan fasinjoji 47 da ma'aikatan jirgin daga jirgin da ya nutse.
Kamfanin Air Niugini ya ce a cikin sanarwar cewa tun ranar Asabar da tsakar rana, kamfanin bai tabbata da lafiyar wani matafiyi namiji ba.
Kamfanin jirgin ya ce yana aiki tare da hukumomin gari, asibitoci da masu bincike don gano mutumin.
